From Creamy Chocolate to Peach Maple Pecan, every smooth spoonful is dairy free, Non-GMO Project Verified and Certified Vegan. Delicious has never looked so good.

ingredients: Cajou base filtered water, cashew nuts, cane sugar, organic coconut oil, organic tapioca syrup, peas protein, sea salt, guar gum, vanilla extract, natural flavors, carobbean gum.contains cashew nuts
